import React from 'react'
import {
    Box,
    Container,
    Row,
    Column,
    FooterLink,
    Heading,
  } from "./FooterStyles";
  
const Footer = () => {
    return (
        <footer>
            
            <row>
          <Column>
            <Heading>About Us</Heading>
            <FooterLink href="#">Aim</FooterLink>
            <FooterLink href="#">Vision</FooterLink>
            <FooterLink href="#">Testimonials</FooterLink>
          </Column>
            
            </row>
    </footer>
    )
}

export default Footer
